FBIS4-33953 "drlat114_r_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-114 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 Peru Economy Minister Attends Seminar in London Economy Minister Attends Seminar in London PY1006220794 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network in Spanish 1800 GMT 10 Jun 94 PY1006220794 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network Spanish BFN [Text] Economy Minister Jorge Camet said today in London that Peru is a secure and stable country for investments, and that its people have regained their faith. Minister Camet is attending a conference on Latin America organized by the Inter-American Development Bank and the HERALD TRIBUNE in London. Camet added that in the next 18 months all state companies, including Petroperu [State Petroleum Agency], Solgas [Compania Peruana de Gas S.A.--Peruvian Natural Gas Company Inc.], Petromar [Petroleos del Mar S.A.--Off-shore Oil Drilling Inc.], Electroperu [Peruvian State Electric Power Company, Inc.], and Sedapal [National Potable Water and Sewage Service] will be privatized.
